# Arrivo environment variables
#
# None are required. All plan content (briefings, itineraries, phrases,
# emergency info, facts for every country) is bundled offline, so the app runs
# fully without any keys or network.

# OPTIONAL — cinematic destination photography (Unsplash). Without it, the app
# still shows real photos via a keyless Wikimedia fallback, then a branded
# gradient. Adding a key upgrades photo quality/variety.
# Get a free key at https://unsplash.com/developers
UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY=
